txt.en: You have weakened many support beams within the Towers of the Teeth. Your efforts will surely affect the Enemy gathered here.
The crumbling towers of Carchost and Narchost are held up by hastily constructed support beams. Weakening the beams could possibly collapse parts of the towers' interiors.
Weakened many support beams in the Towers of the Teeth.
Enter the Towers of the Teeth
This support beam looks as if it could be easily weakened with a few blows.
The Towers of the Teeth are located in the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should weaken support beams in the Towers of the Teeth.
